{"tid":1238815,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[上面做緊野]滬倫通無人講？","createTime":"2019-06-18T03:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T11:14:32.000Z","uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a5baa53b02354e6709eb033bc9f6f2d24e9ffd9a","tid":1238815,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"【滬倫通】華泰証券GDR今日在倫敦上市 (12:46)<br />\n文章日期：2019年6月17日<br />\n<br />\n華泰証券(6886)GDR(Global Depositary Receipt，全球預託證券)將於今日在倫敦上市，代表「滬倫通」正式啟動。<br />\n<br />\n「滬倫通」有別於「深港通」及「滬港通」，由於英國與上海的時差關係，因此採用預託證券的方式，情況相當於部份港股於美國發行美國預託證券(ADR)。<br />\n<br />\n華泰於中港兩地均有上市，因此，今次「滬倫通」下的預託股份是來自A股市場而非港股，據早前華泰的公告，本次GDR發行量為7501萬份，相當於7.5億股A股，集資15.38億美元，每份GDR發行價為20.5美元。<br />\n<br />\n華泰將成為首隻透過「滬倫通」於倫敦上市的A股，據早前報道，英國的匯控(0005)則有機會成為首隻在A股上市的英國公司。<br />\n<br />\n華泰原計劃是在去年12月上市，但因技術問題而延遲，據華爾街日報報道，知情人士當時透露，推遲的原因是英國脫歐不確定性以及其他問題。<br />\n<br />\n另外，英國財政部表示，在上海證交所上市的公司中有260家公司可能有資格在倫敦上市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1560747922012&amp;issue=20190617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1560747922012%26issue%3D20190617&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXris81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=003115df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1560747922012%26issue%3D20190617&h=61956a68\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1560747922012&amp;issue=20190617</a>"},{"pid":"fa0c801f00611b596f72e4b2ff9c5c941cc36b3d","tid":1238815,"uid":237562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"英國狗又奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a51e1d693c415b7e0c07a6a93eda74aa37930e","tid":1238815,"uid":203889,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fa0c801f00611b596f72e4b2ff9c5c941cc36b3d","tid":1238815,"uid":237562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"英國狗又奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"所以唔駛旨意佢地做任何野住<br />\n<br />\n德國先醒<br />\n表面上唔出聲，仲同你傾deal<br />\n但暗地做緊實事"},{"pid":"cead3b75c51da0f41b07aaa0332b7fa9385afdb7","tid":1238815,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:14:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}